8e57176d94b6a44dcd1336849731fa5bc79c2e53af21b47e5a271f012270f5b1 ``` Here's how to use it: **Base URL:** `https://api.datamartgh.shop/api/developer` â†— **Auth header:** add `X-API-Key: <your key>` to every request. **Key endpoints:** - Check balance: `GET /balance` - Buy data: `POST /purchase` with `{phoneNumber, network, capacity, gateway:"wallet"}` - Bulk orders (up to 50): `POST /bulk-purchase` - Check order: `GET /order-status/:reference` **Networks:** YELLO (MTN), TELECEL, AT_PREMIUM. The API pays from your wallet, so keep it topped up at https://www.datamartgh.shop/topup â†— . Also send an `X-Idempotency-Key` header on each request so retries never double-charge. Full docs and examples here: https://www.datamartgh.shop/api-doc â†—
